text: David Pryor (3 February 1870 - 3 January 1937) was an Australian cricketer. He played five first-class matches for New South Wales in 1895/96. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1870 births Category:1937 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
